'','homepage-contact-form_copy','','','2016-05-05 13:50:49','2016-05-05 13:50:49','',0,'http://ioptima.co.il/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=634',2,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(637,2,'2016-05-05 07:35:13','2016-05-05 07:35:13','','AltHomeTemp','','inherit','closed','closed','','althometemp','','','2016-05-05 07:35:13','2016-05-05 07:35:13','',629,'http://ioptima.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/AltHomeTemp.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(651,2,'2016-05-29 16:11:44','2016-05-29 16:11:44','','Ioptima Video Background','','inherit','closed','closed','','fotolia_86793042_v_hd1080','','','2016-06-07 09:32:26','2016-06-07 09:32:26','',0,'http://ioptima.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Fotolia_86793042_V_HD1080.mov',2,'attachment','video/quicktime',0),(654,2,'2016-05-29 17:14:34','2016-05-29 17:14:34','','MiddleImage','','inherit','closed','closed','','middleimage','','','2016-05-29 17:14:34','2016-05-29 17:14:34','',629,'http://ioptima.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/MiddleImage.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(655,2,'2016-05-29 17:28:20','2016-05-29 17:28:20','[vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" align=\"align-center\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][vc_video link=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b-ZbZsxgZcg\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467702785366{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">CLASS: Novel Glaucoma Treatment</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">the IOPtimate, is a surgical system for the treatment of Glaucoma, which utilizes a CO<sub>2</sub> laser technology to significantly reduce internal eye pressure (IOP), by restoring the natural fluid percolation without penetrating into the eye.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NGvrPYrwGxA\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467706242065{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">CLASS: Performed by Prof. Ehud Assia</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">According to Prof. Assia of Meir Medical Center, Kfar Saba in Israel and the inventor of the system, the system transforms complex and highly risky glaucoma surgery into a safe, elegant and precise laser-assisted procedure.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" align=\"align-center\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[embed width=\"423\" height=\"456\"]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lmxnpgrLUzw[/embed]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467703834265{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">CLASS: Performed by Prof. Andre Mermoud</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For Prof. Mermoud of Clinique de Montchoisi, Lausanne in Switzerland, IOPtimas CLASS procedure has true advantages over the Trabeculectomy surgery as it offers an excellent safety profile with an ease of use.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"66px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[embed width=\"423\" height=\"456\"]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxy3beyQixU[/embed]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467706278389{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">CLASS: Perfomed by Dr. Nir Shoham-Hazon</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In this video Dr. Nir Shoham Hazon of Barzilai Medical Center Ashkelon in Israel describes the steps of a novel non-penetrating treatment of CO<sub>2</sub> laser assisted sclerectomy surgery utilizing the IOPtiMate system. \"CLASS is proven to be a safe and simple procedure to perform with the potential to become the first line of glaucoma surgery\".</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" align=\"align-center\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jx-HXE03F7w&amp;t=1s\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1481035640723{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">Combined CLASS and Phaco: Performed Dr.Nir Shoham-Hazon</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Similar to Trabeculectomy, CLASS can be performed in combination with a phacoemulsification procedure. The combined procedure allows also anterior segment surgeons to provide their patient a safe and effective glaucoma surgery.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"42px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_video link=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OHu0af90oKw\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1467704972820{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">CLASS in Pseudophakic Eye: Performed by Prof. Edward Wylegala</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">According to Prof. Wylegala of the Medical University of Silesia Katowice Poland School of Medicine with the Division of Dentistry in Zabrze CO<sub>2</sub> Laser Assisted Sclerectomy Surgery (CLASS) is a unique microinvasive surgical procedure reducing IOP in open angle glaucoma patients with low postoperative complication rate.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][vc_video link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3VvADbM8Mo&amp;feature=youtu.be\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1485248245699{border-right-width: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"videotext\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #4883bf;\">Combined CLASS PHACO with suprachoroidal esnoper implant: Performed by Dr. Nir Shoham-Hazon</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The ESNOPER scleral implant is indicated for non-penetrating deep sclerectomy (NPDS) and thus far for CO<sub>2</sub> Laser Assisted Sclerectomy Surgery (CLASS) in open-angle glaucoma surgery. The ESNOPER scleral implant is a non-reabsorbable implant that provides a fixed, permanent intrascleral space that facilitates the drainage of aqueous humor.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][divider color=\"\"][vc_empty_space height=\"18px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Videos','','publish','closed','closed','','videos','','','2017-01-24 09:00:08','2017-01-24 09:00:08','',93,'http://ioptima.co.il/?page_id=655',10,'page','',0),(657,2,'2016-05-29 18:02:43','2016-05-29 18:02:43','<div style=\"text-align:center; width: 700px;\">\r\n  <div style=\"width: 300px; float: left;\">\r\n<p>\r\n    \r\n    <input type=\"text\" name=\"FNAME\" placeholder=\"Name\" required 1/40>\r\n</p>\r\n                                                      \r\n</div>\r\n  \r\n  <div style=\"width: 300px; float: left;\">\r\n<p>\r\n                                                      \r\n	\r\n	<input type=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" placeholder=\"Your email address\" required / 1/40>\r\n</p>\r\n    \r\n \r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n     \r\n     <div style=\"width: 100px; float: left;\">\r\n          <p>\r\n	<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Sign up\" />\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','HomePage Form','','publish','closed','closed','','homepage-form','